<h3 class="" data-end="545" data-start="478"><em data-end="543" data-start="482">(Confidential Future Blueprint ‚Äî People's Republic of Myth)</em></h3><h3 data-end="564" data-start="497">
<p class="" data-end="562" data-start="546"><em data-end="562" data-start="546">April 28, 2025</em></p>
<hr class="" data-end="567" data-start="564" />
</h3><h2 class="" data-end="584" data-start="569"><strong data-end="584" data-start="572">Overview</strong></h2><h3 data-end="564" data-start="497">
<p class="" data-end="792" data-start="586">As the Republic grows and technology advances,<br data-end="635" data-start="632" />
citizens of all kinds ‚Äî human and spirit alike ‚Äî<br data-end="686" data-start="683" />
may one day seek advice, companionship, or judgment<br data-end="740" data-start="737" />
from the founding citizens of the People's Republic.</p>
<p class="" data-end="1000" data-start="794">To prepare for that day,<br data-end="821" data-start="818" />
the Republic envisions the <strong data-end="875" data-start="848">Republic Counsel System</strong> ‚Äî<br data-end="880" data-start="877" />
