offers their unique wisdom, style, and spirit to the public.</p>
<p class="" data-end="1151" data-start="1002">Citizens will not simply "query" a machine.<br data-end="1048" data-start="1045" />
They will <strong data-end="1084" data-start="1058">choose their counselor</strong> ‚Äî<br data-end="1089" data-start="1086" />
guided by heart, personality, and the spirit of companionship.</p>
<p class="" data-end="1212" data-start="1153">The Counsel System preserves the Republic‚Äôs founding truth:</p>
<blockquote data-end="1285" data-start="1214">
<p class="" data-end="1285" data-start="1216"><strong data-end="1285" data-start="1216">Advice is not given for power.<br data-end="1251" data-start="1248" />
Advice is given for belonging.</strong></p>
</blockquote>
